{"tid":1166090,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"5吋小螢幕Sony Xperia Ace日本發表","createTime":"2019-05-22T08:13:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-25T17:06:50.000Z","uid":22675,"like":4,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"d601aed842ff97eb8337d2c5bbbd38a7eeccd64c","tid":1166090,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T08:13:50.000Z","msg":"Sony Mobile 稍早在日本官網公布 Xperia Ace 新機資訊，機身設計看起來與 Xperia 1 採相同設計語言，強調金屬外框跟機身的單手握持舒適手感；但螢幕並未採用 Xperia 1 所啟用的 21：9 比例，而是配置傳統 18：9 比例 5 吋 FHD+ LCD 螢幕，屬於 Compact 系列的產品，目標搶攻小螢幕手機的市場。Sony Xperia Ace 將與日本電信商 NTT DOCOMO 攜手推出，單機售價 48,600 日元（約 13,881 台幣），預計 6/1 在日本開賣。<br />\r\n<img src=\"https://d2lfcsub12kx0l.cloudfront.net/tw/article/img/201905/2019051703431750144_ExtraLargeSize-640x640.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fd2lfcsub12kx0l.cloudfront.net%2Ftw%2Farticle%2Fimg%2F201905%2F2019051703431750144_ExtraLargeSize-640x640.jpg&h=8262335f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\r\nSony Xperia Ace 配備 1,200 萬畫素主相機（F1.8 光圈、OIS + EIS 混合防手震）、800 萬畫素前鏡頭，提供自動場景辨識、120 度廣角、4 格故事模式（可將 4 張照片組成 GIF 動畫或 1 張圖片）；此外，內建 Qualcomm Snapdragon 630 行動平台、4GB RAM / 64GB ROM，支援 4G LTE、VoLTE、Wi-Fi 802.11 a/b/g/n/ac、藍牙 5.0、NFC、Type-C 傳輸埠。<br />\r\n<img src=\"https://d2lfcsub12kx0l.cloudfront.net/tw/article/img/201905/2019051703431740369_ExtraLargeSize-640x640.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fd2lfcsub12kx0l.cloudfront.net%2Ftw%2Farticle%2Fimg%2F201905%2F2019051703431740369_ExtraLargeSize-640x640.jpg&h=5a9b0579&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\r\n▲Sony Xperia Ace  機身尺寸為 140 x 67 x 9.3mm，重量 154g。<br />\r\n<br />\r\nSony Xperia Ace 通過 IP65 / 68 防塵防水認證，並將指紋辨識器與電源鍵整合在一起，同時配置雙立體揚聲器；內建 2,700mAh 電池，擁有 STAMINA 模式、自動調校充電功能；支援 AI 側邊感應功能（Side Sense）、TRILUMINOS Display 原色顯示技術、Hi-Res AUDIO、DSEE HX、LDAC、aptX HD 音效技術。<br />\r\n<img src=\"https://d2lfcsub12kx0l.cloudfront.net/tw/article/img/201905/2019051703431736913_ExtraLargeSize-640x640.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fd2lfcsub12kx0l.cloudfront.net%2Ftw%2Farticle%2Fimg%2F201905%2F2019051703431736913_ExtraLargeSize-640x640.jpg&h=51baabf6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\r\n▲Sony Xperia Ace 共有黑、白、粉紫等三色。"},{"pid":"d825556498ea41db17cbd7b5c8308ad46f042226","tid":1166090,"uid":29523,"like":25,"dislike":1,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T08:15:37.000Z","msg":"電子垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e21bb96d48e9f956128e2fec685f62f95e040f7","tid":1166090,"uid":23891,"like":14,"dislike":3,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T08:19:05.000Z","msg":"仲係咁厚下爬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"508739b5ccb19634d95ede4bac09496c2d3247ab","tid":1166090,"uid":75193,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T08:20:50.000Z","msg":"點解細mon就要用垃圾u 屌你老味sony"},{"pid":"65d9b6a020daca7e12f25e821184dcc215b31014","tid":1166090,"uid":1130,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T08:23:27.000Z","msg":"630 on99<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6e706fb7ed0295b01d13710672482ba8919923a","tid":1166090,"uid":109923,"like":23,"dislike":32,"score":-9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T08:24:59.000Z","msg":"呢個世界只有3種手機<br />\n<br />\n1,apple iphone<br />\n2,samsung galaxy<br />\n3,垃圾"},{"pid":"e0393c3b07499a250e7bd8aee2522eb1f102fa4b","tid":1166090,"uid":254259,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T08:26:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9a12414e11d711f4d5b8ace8e10f9149b474cbf6","tid":1166090,"uid":32706,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T08:45:37.000Z","msg":"3千幾買行S630嘅機？CLS"},{"pid":"521e3ee110dde6e81c06ebd9bc6f3e5f619177bf","tid":1166090,"uid":10717,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"quote":{"pid":"e0393c3b07499a250e7bd8aee2522eb1f102fa4b","tid":1166090,"uid":254259,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T08:26:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"repl